The paper deals with initializing deep neural networks for document image analysis, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of PCA for initialization is a machine learning technique, which also makes it relevant to sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), and deep learning (cs.DL).
